text:
Ah!
Did you buy the magazine?

You look good in it.
Both you, Saijo-san, and Morino-san.

Thank you!
I'll let them know too!

...But I'm happy, you know... When photos like this
come out, kids in my class are like, "Were you hungry?"

They say stuff like, "When Sonoda is quiet,
she must be thinking about food", you know...!

Oh, how stylish! They captured your serious
thinking-about-food face so beautifully.

Haha, just kidding!
You're actually making a nice face, yeah!
